<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Robert_Louis_Stevenson&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: Life">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Life">Life</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Robert_Louis_Stevenson&action=edit&section=2.php.html" title="Edit section: Childhood">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Childhood">Childhood</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9f/Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg/220px-Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg" width="220" height="263" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9f/Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg/330px-Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9f/Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg/440px-Robert_Louis_Stevenson_daguerreotype_portrait_as_a_child.jpg 2x" /></a>
