<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Robert_Louis_Stevenson&action=edit&section=25.php.html" title="Edit section: Secondary literature">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Secondary_literature">Secondary literature</span></h2>
